to you."],[2485,2606,"You deserve this."],[2698,2873,"I should tell Mark to back off."],[2873,3040,"This is moving too fast."],[3390,3503,"Here to thank me?"],[3624,3707,"Eve..."],[3707,3832,"Made your favorite."],[3832,3987,"I hope we're okay now."],[3987,4087,"I'll call off the"],[4087,4241,"engagement just like you asked."],[4241,4325,"Thanks."],[4462,4675,"Um, let's get you cleaned up."],[4675,4863,"I'll change in the break room."],[6139,6210,"What the hell?"]],"20":[[100,191,"What the hell?"],[417,608,"Mark loves these little games."],[608,800,"Just the two of us."],[930,1109,"Wait, before you go,"],[1109,1238,"make me a coffee."],[1334,1426,"Not happening."],[1539,1747,"Do you know who you're speaking to?"],[1747,1939,"I am the second largest shareholder"],[1939,2052,"in this company,"],[2052,2231,"and I'm Mark's fiancée."],[2231,2281,"I could get you"],[2281,2406,"fired in an instant."],[3541,3616,"Bring it to me."],[4187,4341,"You know, Selena's insurance"],[4341,4517,"hasn't been approved yet,"],[4517,4633,"and disrespecting me"],[4633,4808,"is not going to help you."],[4892,5221,"But I'll give you a chance."],[5526,5613,"Oh, you...."],[5747,5918,"Drink this, and I'll make sure"],[5918,6177,"your daughter gets life-saving surgery."],[6769,6948,"What are you two doing here?"]],"21":[[212,392,"What are you two doing here?"],[450,542,"What's going on Emily?"],[542,775,"Why the hell are you wearing my shirt, Eve?"],[775,946,"Emily's spilled coffee on me."],[946,1092,"I guess she's not too fond of"],[1092,1238,"me wearing your shirt."],[1347,1501,"But you were so rough earlier,"],[1501,1685,"I got soaked so I had to put"],[1685,1935,"something on to cover up the mess."],[1935,2068,"I'm not staying for this."],[2377,2477,"Emily wait."],[2619,2736,"Did you need me for something?"],[2736,2844,"You've done enough making me"],[2844,2977,"supervisor, Mark. I don't need"],[2977,3123,"anything else from you."],[3123,3299,"HR made you a supervisor."],[3299,3503,"That wasn't my call. You earned it."],[3503,3678,"No sorry. The loan is almost"],[3678,3820,"through and then I can pay you back"],[3820,4008,"and we can get a divorce."]],"22":[[387,508,"Divorce?"],[508,667,"Is that really what you want?"],[746,829,"You never thought about"],[829,950,"actually staying with me?"],[1067,1188,"I don't wanna be the third wheel"],[1188,1334,"in your drama, Mark."],[1401,1543,"I have bills to pay and a"],[1543,1701,"daughter to take care of."],[1755,1943,"Emily, don't get the wrong idea."],[1972,2152,"There's nothing going on with Eve."],[2227,2377,"Please trust me."],[2427,2569,"I'll prove it to you."],[2686,2761,"You'll love this."],[2761,2898,"You're gonna love what I got you."],[3215,3370,"Oh! Perfect timing."],[3370,3511,"I'm right around the corner."],[3853,3891,"Feel like"],[3891,4054,"I'm remembering something."]],"23":[[87,187,"Mark, are you okay?"],[275,337,"Wait!"],[337,458,"This necklace..."],[458,604,"It look just like mine."],[604,713,"Mark, what do you remember?"],[884,1009,"Our client, Mr. Thompson, is"],[1009,1080,"waiting for you in the"],[1080,1172,"conference room, boss."],[1430,1493,"I'll see you later."],[1735,2068,"Get your team to tidy up and take"],[2068,2235,"these to the conference room."],[2264,2389,"Mr. Thompson likes the little least"],[2389,2464,"in every room he's"],[2464,2540,"having a meeting in."],[3728,3849,"Bone marrow donation?"],[3920,4095,"Mark's donating bone marrow for"],[4095,4229,"that bitch's kid?"],[4229,4371,"No way in hell."],[4371,4562,"This is his wife. Mark's not"],[4562,4713,"available right now."],[4713,4879,"We're trying for a baby."],[4879,5117,"He will not be donated."]],"24":[[462,704,"So, we've secured a 200 million dollar"],[704,784,"investment"],[784,925,"for a new overseas branch."],[1142,1259,"Sir,"],[1259,1355,"what's wrong?"],[1530,1626,"What's wrong?"],[1739,1847,"Lilies?"],[1847,2010,"I said no Lilies?"],[2010,2127,"Who the hell brought these in?"],[2127,2198,"Emily did."],[2198,2227,"What?"],[2227,2327,"No, I uh..."],[2327,2498,"If anything happens to Mr. Thompson,"],[2498,2660,"we are suing your company."],[2660,2911,"Mr. Thompson, we are so sorry."],[2911,3048,"My fiancé would personally"],[3048,3165,"escort you to the hospital."],[3165,3311,"Tyler, prep the car."],[3311,3390,"We'll get Mr. Thompson"],[3390,3536,"to a specialist ASAP."],[3895,4012,"Did you try to kill"],[4012,4175,"our client, Emily?"],[4175,4283,"Anna, you told me to bring the"],[4283,4375,"Lilies in the room."],[4441,4504,"Are you really"],[4504,4696,"trying to smear Anna?"],[4729,4813,"Oh, please... I know"],[4813,4925,"you two are in on it."],[4992,5084,"You're trying to blame your"],[5084,5226,"incompetence on us?"],[5259,5417,"Maybe if you spent less time trying"],[5417,5563,"to seduce my fiancé,"],[5563,5726,"you could actually do your job."],[5759,5964,"Emily is always the problem."],[5964,6081,"We should've thrown her out"],[6081,6268,"on the street ages ago."],[6706,6760,"Jen,"],[6760,6861,"you saw me take the Lilies"],[6861,6969,"out of the room, right?"],[6969,7115,"I saw Emily put the"],[7115,7198,"Lilies on the table."]],"25":[[0,158,"I saw Emily put the Lilies"],[158,237,"on the table."],[417,492,"What?"],[492,596,"Jen, why are you lying?"],[667,721,"I'm sorry."],[950,1088,"Trying to run away from"],[1088,1234,"the mess that you made?"],[1234,1368,"I didn't do anything."],[1368,1447,"Let me talk to Mark."],[1447,1726,"Mark, do you really think he cares?"],[1726,1839,"Stop dreaming."],[1839,1981,"He left me to handle this."],[1981,2227,"He doesn't give a shit about you."],[2227,2510,"You've ruined everything, Emily."],[2510,2619,"Because of you,"],[2619,2882,"Selena's insurance is cancelled."],[3002,3215,"Selena's not getting treatment."],[3215,3411,"What? Please, you can't."],[3411,3586,"Selena's surgery is happening soon."],[3586,3645,"Please, you can't do this."],[3645,3737,"You can't."]],"26":[[0,200,"What? Please, you can't."],[200,354,"Selena's surgery is happening soon."],[354,433,"Please, you can't do this."],[433,487,"You can't."],[646,800,"Anna, put your"],[800,988,"supervisor's head in the bucket."],[1155,1343,"You're really"],[1343,1555,"forcing our hands, Emily."],[1618,1735,"Let me fucking go!"],[1735,1826,"Let's see how you're gonna"],[1826,1910,"seduce your boss"],[1910,2006,"smelling like piss."],[2006,2127,"I didn't seduce anyone!"],[2127,2268,"Oh no, then how did you get the"],[2268,2473,"supervisor position by yourself?"],[2473,2677,"Please Emily. Save us all the time."],[2677,2790,"Get your head into the bucket."],[3136,3332,"Mark... where are you?"],[3332,3436,"I need you..."],[3490,3616,"Get the fuck off of her!"]],"27":[[734,863,"How you feeling?"],[863,946,"I'm fine."],[984,1117,"What happened to the client? Is he..."],[1117,1205,"He's fine."],[1205,1280,"Don't worry."],[1343,1434,"Linda's fired."],[1434,1514,"Anna's demoted."],[1514,1655,"Eve's been dealt with."],[1655,1793,"I won't let them hurt you again."],[2039,2164,"You've been through hell."],[2252,2356,"I'll fix this."],[2398,2489,"As for Selena, I'm"],[2489,2590,"waiting on the hospital."],[2610,2711,"If I'm a match,"],[2711,2831,"I'll give her my marrow."],[2907,3036,"And if not,"],[3036,3136,"I'll find another way."],[3190,3253,"Thank you."],[3382,3524,"I don't know how to repay you."],[3582,3720,"No need to repay me."],[3762,3874,"Anything for you."],[3933,4024,"Just rest."],[4058,4191,"I'll take care of everything."]],"28":[[20,95,"Mark,"],[166,304,"I don't know how to thank you."],[1297,1451,"You sure?"],[1539,1680,"I don't know. I haven't fallen for"],[1680,1826,"someone in such a long time."],[1910,2072,"Let me be that someone."],[2072,2173,"I'm here for you."],[2227,2469,"I know, Mark. I care about you."],[3461,3620,"No worries."],[3620,3753,"When you're ready,"],[3753,3862,"I'll be here."],[4571,4721,"Selena's loan is approved."]],"29":[[45,175,"Selena's loan is approved."],[262,350,"I gotta get to the hospital."],[350,442,"Dr. Grey's waiting."],[475,654,"Relax. I told you. I've got"],[654,759,"everything covered."],[759,855,"Trust me."],[1451,1580,"I gotta take this real quick."],[1739,1835,"Dr. Grey?"],[1993,2122,"I got the money."],[2122,2243,"We can start the application now."],[2285,2377,"Emily."],[2494,2669,"We don't have a match for Selena."],[2669,2811,"What?"],[2811,2907,"What about Mark's?"],[2907,3015,"Mark withdrew."],[3090,3244,"His wife was concerned about their"],[3244,3370,"plans for a child."],[3370,3478,"A child?"],[3478,3707,"Mark never mentioned kids with me."],[4183,4325,"Did you really think he was just"],[4325,4466,"gonna donate bone marrow"],[4466,4608,"for some random kid?"]],"30":[[79,183,"I'm not part of"],[183,342,"your pathetic drama."],[342,467,"What exactly are you playing at?"],[467,538,"Mark and I will have a"],[538,671,"child of our own soon."],[717,821,"And you're just some pathetic"],[821,1046,"little toy he's playing with."],[1046,1167,"But don't worry, darling."],[1167,1343,"I'll still save Selena."],[1343,1476,"But first, you have to let me do"],[1476,1601,"something to you."],[2644,2794,"Here's the full report, sir."],[3019,3219,"But there was something else."],[3269,3349,"What is it?"],[3399,3582,"Well, you wanted me to look into"],[3582,3724,"Emily's past,"],[3724,3974,"but it seems like she's erased it."],[3974,4091,"There's almost nothing."],[4208,4341,"So what did you find?"],[4379,4537,"She went to school with you,"],[4537,4708,"but as soon as you had your accident,"],[4708,4859,"she dropped out."],[4859,4984,"So you're saying"],[4984,5125,"I probably knew her?"]],"31":[[62,133,"Perhaps you should"],[133,246,"just ask her that yourself, sir."],[467,688,"Oh shit, I gotta get back to her."],[1180,1330,"What the fuck?"],[1488,1797,"Oh darling, you look terrible."],[1872,2010,"You didn't think you could just walk away,"],[2010,2106,"did you?"],[2147,2293,"Crazy bitch, what did you do?"],[2335,2464,"What did I do?"],[2519,2577,"I'm just taking"],[2577,2711,"care of a few things."],[2907,3132,"Where's Mark? Where's Selena?"],[3132,3286,"Oh don't worry,"],[3286,3524,"I'll take good care of them."],[3524,3661,"But first I need you to"],[3661,3824,"be a good girl for me."],[3874,4049,"No, let me go!"],[4049,4250,"Calm down, I'm not gonna kill you."],[4250,4408,"I'm just putting you to sleep."],[4408,4579,"And no one will be able to find you"],[4579,4783,"while I take back what's mine."],[4783,5113,"No, no, let me go."],[5150,5438,"No, no, no, let me go."],[5472,5572,"Hey, no!"],[5668,5789,"Help, help, help!"],[5826,6047,"Touch her... and you both dead."]],"32":[[354,504,"Don't worry, I got you."],[1438,1589,"Sir, you've been confirmed."],[1634,1739,"Eve orchestrated everything."],[1860,1951,"We're terminating all contracts"],[1951,2106,"with attorneys."],[2152,2243,"But sir, the losses."],[2248,2298,"I don't care."],[2327,2448,"No one messes with my girl."],[2531,2665,"Send Eve to New Zealand."],[2665,2711,"I don't want her"],[2711,2827,"anywhere near Emily."],[3591,3716,"Take all the time you need."],[3716,3820,"I'm fine."],[3849,3941,"Selena's waiting for me,"],[3941,4029,"I gotta go home."],[4066,4187,"Dr. Grey’s here with a new"],[4187,4308,"treatment plan for Selena."],[4350,4529,"Meds care the best team."],[4554,4667,"I've got it all covered."],[4667,4750,"I got you too."],[4767,4934,"I appreciate it, Mark, but we're"],[4934,5050,"just in a contract."],[5050,5130,"Nothing more."],[5130,5213,"This was never just"],[5213,5347,"a contract, Emily."],[5347,5488,"You're my wife."],[5488,5676,"I won't let anyone hurt you again."],[6181,6285,"I trust you."],[7282,7415,"What are you doing?"]],"33":[[350,596,"See, I'm here. You're safe now."],[1101,1176,"I'll always look"],[1176,1468,"after you, no matter what."],[2598,2823,"Selena is stable after treatment."],[2952,3094,"No need for surgery."],[3228,3390,"She'll be ready for discharge soon."],[3390,3453,"Oh, that's amazing."],[3453,3603,"Thank you so much, Dr. Gray."],[3641,3682,"Excuse me."],[3799,3887,"Did you hear that, sweetie?"],[3887,3970,"You're going home soon."]],"34":[[1263,1488,"So, does this mean we're all gonna"],[1488,1614,"live together now?"],[1614,1726,"Mom and Dad?"],[1826,1960,"Yes, sweetheart."],[1960,2114,"Untill you get tired of us?"],[2239,2331,"Sweetie..."],[2331,2535,"The food here is awful."],[2610,2686,"Can one of you two"],[2686,2848,"get me a burger or something?"],[2911,2998,"Please."],[2998,3090,"Yes."],[3090,3199,"You little Munchkin."],[3607,3695,"Stop following me!"],[3695,3791,"I'll call the cops."],[3849,3937,"Emily!"],[4062,4112,"Hey, What's wrong?"],[4112,4170,"You okay?"],[4212,4371,"Yeah, it's just a wrong number."],[4425,4579,"Hey, I want to ask you something."],[4608,4679,"You recognize the"],[4679,4854,"trophy in my office."],[4854,4963,"Were we at the same school?"]],"35":[[20,137,"Were we at the same school?"],[221,304,"Um..."],[563,775,"No, I didn't go to college."],[855,967,"I can't let Mark know..."],[967,1126,"Not about my past,"],[1126,1238,"all that shame."],[1343,1401,"You can tell me"],[1401,1593,"anything, you know. I won't judge."],[1947,2068,"Hey, watch out!"],[2239,2348,"Hey, I promised Selena"],[2348,2394,"I'd look after..."],[2394,2460,"Emily?"],[2686,2773,"Don't push me away."],[2998,3119,"Please."],[3953,4033,"Wow."],[4116,4237,"Did you make all this?"]],"36":[[29,216,"I've never really felt love before"],[279,400,"until I met you."],[525,650,"I don't know."],[650,896,"I might not deserve your love."],[946,1096,"Loving you feels right."],[1151,1372,"It's like something's telling me"],[1372,1493,"you're the one."],[2235,2369,"You want to rate my cooking?"],[2802,2927,"This is amazing."],[2927,3040,"I'm glad you like it."],[3078,3361,"From now on, I can be your private chef"],[3407,3536,"every single day."],[3741,3895,"I would love that."],[3895,3978,"Really."],[4813,5021,"I feel like I've known you for years."],[5839,5960,"Then don't let me go."]],"37":[[95,367,"This feels so right."],[658,771,"Emily?"],[2022,2256,"What the hell did I do last night?"],[2598,2669,"I didn't mean to."],[2727,2852,"I'm ... No idea what I'm doing..."],[2932,3057,"Running already?"],[3057,3153,"After the last night?"],[3207,3353,"Not running. I gotta work."],[3399,3549,"Emily, I'll survive you"],[3549,3707,"if you're late for work for one day."],[3766,3908,"Really gotta go."],[3970,4095,"Well, I'm your husband."],[4095,4316,"Don't I at least deserve a good morning kiss?"],[4775,4833,"There."],[4833,4896,"Are you happy now?"],[5030,5142,"Mark, I really gotta go."],[5142,5217,"Don't be late."],[5217,5309,"I'll drive you."],[5309,5480,"I can't let my wife leave my side."],[6719,6790,"Look who finally"],[6790,6965,"decided to show up to work."]],"38":[[0,137,"Watch your mouth, Anna."],[137,246,"You're demoted."],[246,333,"Start talking to your"],[333,487,"superior with some respect."],[571,692,"I'm Eve's cousin."],[738,784,"What do you think"],[784,925,"Mr. Cardmon gonna do?"],[925,1017,"Fire me?"],[1038,1172,"What if I do?"],[1234,1376,"Boss."],[1376,1509,"What?"],[1509,1643,"What are you saying?"],[1668,1805,"Cross Emily again, you're out."],[1805,1976,"I don't care who your cousin is."],[1976,2093,"Here at Cardmon Enterprise,"],[2093,2273,"we treat everyone the same."],[2314,2427,"Well, hold on."],[2427,2540,"I'm not hearing an apology now,"],[2540,2610,"do I?"],[2819,3094,"I'm sorry, Mr. Cardmon."],[3094,3407,"No, not to me. To her."],[3653,3812,"I'm sorry, Emily,"],[3812,4049,"for dropping the coffee"],[4049,4295,"and accusing you."],[4346,4533,"It's fine, Anna. I'm just on duty."],[4575,4742,"You're here for your work."],[4742,4900,"Not who you're related to."],[4900,5042,"And Emily, she's ..."]],"39":[[4,145,"And Emily, well she's my..."],[371,483,"Consider yourself warned."],[1176,1334,"Why won't you let me go public?"],[1334,1380,"If you did,"],[1380,1501,"no one would dare mess with you."],[1501,1668,"I'd give you and Selena everything."],[1668,1856,"I can take care of Selena myself."],[1856,1997,"We agreed to keep it simple."],[1997,2089,"Remember?"],[2089,2168,"Unless I don't want to get dragged"],[2168,2298,"into your mess with Eve."],[2298,2473,"I get it, but it still hurts."],[2473,2590,"You're making things way harder"],[2590,2719,"than I need to be."],[3148,3261,"Happy now?"]],"40":[[517,658,"18 minutes, happy?"],[658,846,"Who told you to drive like that?"],[846,1009,"Forget your bonus this month."],[1009,1134,"But sir...You told me to hurry."],[2252,2356,"Welcome home!"],[2427,2502,"Sweetie."],[2548,2640,"How's the house?"],[2640,2744,"If it's too small, we can find a"],[2744,2827,"bigger one tomorrow."],[2827,3015,"This place is like a castle."],[3015,3094,"I love it."],[3165,3274,"Go check out your room."],[3274,3370,"I'll sleep beside you tonight."],[3370,3499,"I miss our late night chats."],[3557,3661,"I'm off to bed."],[3703,3824,"I think dad needs you a"],[3824,3949,"little more than I do."],[3999,4158,"Maybe I'll get a little sister soon."]],"41":[[100,208,"Dad, do you have any pics"],[208,354,"from when you were young?"],[354,487,"I'm gotta see if I got"],[487,754,"any of your elite CEO genes."],[754,900,"You actually look more like me."],[900,1159,"No, look at this jaw and this face."],[1159,1418,"It's total Cardman material."],[1580,1856,"Mom, that's literally me."],[1856,2047,"Oh, my God."],[2047,2214,"You really do look like him."],[2214,2381,"That's kind of scary, actually."],[2573,2815,"Oh, um, I can get it."],[2915,2998,"Selena, do you mind"],[2998,3111,"grabbing the photo?"],[3111,3169,"Yeah."],[4170,4400,"Damn, Em, You're looking good."],[4450,4583,"Miss me?"]],"42":[[41,120,"Wow."],[237,417,"You really leveled up, huh?"],[417,554,"Heard you found yourself a rich guy."],[554,663,"What do you want?"],[663,804,"Just here to see my daughter."],[804,955,"He's not here, is he?"],[955,1071,"Does he know about..."],[1071,1155,"you know"],[1155,1247,"us?"],[1301,1472,"There is no \"us\"."],[1514,1626,"Get the hell out."],[1710,1818,"Hey, wait here."],[1818,1926,"I'll check on your mom."],[2039,2164,"Don't be that way."],[2239,2452,"Unless you wanna pay me to disappear."],[2990,3044,"Wait."],[3044,3123,"That's mom and dad"],[3123,3236,"when they were young."],[3319,3432,"This doesn't feel right."],[3582,3691,"Oh, here he comes."],[3691,3824,"The rich guy."]],"43":[[0,183,"You know Selena is my daughter, right?"],[283,346,"He's lying."],[346,462,"Selena isn't his!"],[462,508,"Dad?"],[567,621,"You were born at"],[621,750,"Queen Valley Hospital."],[838,959,"I was there. I named you."],[1021,1180,"You've got a birthmark, right?"],[1180,1343,"He's just screwing with us."],[1343,1505,"Bet he doesn't even know about it."],[1505,1576,"So you need to get the"],[1576,1730,"fuck out of my house."],[1826,2001,"You know she's a con-artist, right?"],[2089,2168,"Leave."],[2473,2569,"This isn't over."],[2815,2957,"I'm taking my daughter back."]],"44":[[312,412,"I'm so sorry."],[412,592,"I didn't think my ex would show up."],[592,734,"I don't buy any of his bullshit."],[734,871,"So that walking red flag"],[871,1067,"is my biological dad?"],[1113,1242,"Wow, tragic."],[1242,1422,"At least that explains my trust issues."],[1422,1555,"I didn't marry for love."],[1555,1685,"I had no choice."],[1685,1797,"My boyfriend disappeared after"],[1797,1901,"I got pregnant,"],[1901,2035,"and I dropped out and kept the baby."],[2035,2135,"You don't have to explain."],[2135,2231,"I get it."],[2231,2331,"William was my neighbor,"],[2331,2498,"and he took me to the hospital."],[2498,2681,"Selena has a blood disorder,"],[2681,2898,"and William claimed to be a sailor."],[2898,3036,"Said we should fake the marriage"],[3036,3190,"for her insurance."],[3219,3470,"But then he drank too much"],[3470,3620,"and got violent,"],[3620,3949,"and that's why I left him."],[3949,4108,"Whatever happened, you're here now."],[4154,4254,"I got you."],[4254,4446,"I never wanted you to know any of this."]],"45":[[0,175,"Whatever happened, you're here now."],[233,312,"I got you."],[312,525,"I never wanted you to know any of this."],[575,734,"It's not your fault."],[734,946,"You did what you had to for Selena."],[946,1096,"You two are safe now."],[1096,1280,"You're my daughter, Selena."],[1280,1351,"And I'll love you"],[1351,1530,"as much as I love your mom."],[2515,2635,"Shop away ladies."],[2635,2777,"Everything's on me."],[2777,2898,"We don't need anything."],[2898,3019,"Try the newest collection."],[3019,3244,"Oh my god, seriously?"],[3244,3361,"It's like a movie."],[3361,3528,"I'm practically a princess!"],[3528,3741,"Of course, my princess."]],"46":[[287,379,"Selena!"],[379,467,"Morning, Mom!"],[467,604,"What are you doing here?"],[604,721,"Shouldn't you be resting?"],[721,892,"Dad said I could intern."],[892,1021,"I'm totally fine, Mom."],[1021,1163,"Just don't let anyone know that"],[1163,1267,"your father's the boss, all right?"],[1267,1413,"We don't need that kind of attention."],[1413,1514,"Who's that?"],[1514,1647,"That's Emily's daughter."],[1647,1743,"Selena."],[1743,1914,"Emily drugged the CEO."],[1914,2110,"She almost got me fired."],[2110,2289,"And now she's bringing her daughter here,"],[2289,2423,"disrespecting you."],[2494,2627,"Go back to work, Anna."],[2756,2915,"Fresh pastries for my girl."],[3136,3286,"Thanks dad!"],[3286,3428,"Take it easy, okay?"],[3428,3549,"If you feel sick, go home."],[3549,3641,"Your mom will get mad at me if you..."],[3641,3799,"I am fine."],[3799,3908,"I'm not a kid."],[3908,4049,"Go be a CEO or whatever."],[4049,4175,"I got this."]],"47":[[316,437,"First Emily..."],[437,638,"now her brat too?"],[638,855,"No wonder Mark’s cutting me off."],[3607,3791,"Who the hell did this?"],[3791,3987,"What's going on here?"],[3987,4104,"Looks like there's no room"],[4104,4204,"for you here."],[4204,4316,"Just like your mother."],[4454,4604,"What is wrong with you?"],[4713,4909,"Everyone's listening sweetheart."],[4909,5009,"Why don't you tell them how you"],[5009,5188,"actually got this job?"],[5263,5342,"I..."]],"48":[[108,304,"Everyone's listening sweetheart."],[304,404,"Why don't you tell them how you"],[404,583,"actually got this job?"],[1096,1213,"Hey, hey!"],[1213,1368,"Get your hands off of her!"],[1368,1501,"Shouldn't you be in New Zealand, Eve?"],[1501,1622,"What the hell are you doing here?"],[1622,1710,"Just stopping a little"],[1710,1956,"mother-daughter scam operation."],[1956,2001,"Duh..."],[2281,2356,"Stop!"],[2506,2606,"Hey, back off!"],[2973,3065,"Stay away from her!"],[3219,3319,"What are you waiting for?"],[3407,3570,"Get your cameras out! Let's get a"],[3570,3724,"live stream going."],[3851,3963,"Stop, stop it!"],[4041,4149,"Enough!"],[4245,4404,"Back to work now."]],"49":[[0,116,"Back to work now."],[412,554,"Wait, I'm Eve's cousin."],[554,625,"I don't give a damn"],[625,742,"who you're related to."],[742,846,"You're fired."],[846,934,"Anyone who messes with"],[934,1121,"Selena and Emily will pay."],[1222,1272,"Take her away."],[1355,1526,"What? No! Wait!"],[1551,1747,"Guys, come on."],[1747,1956,"Mark, they were provoking me."],[1956,2164,"You’re banned from every Cardmon property."],[2164,2427,"No more deals, no more contracts,"],[2427,2552,"no more you."],[2552,2715,"You can't do that."],[2715,2932,"My team runs the Core Tech."],[2932,3098,"The clients will never stand for it."],[3098,3345,"You'll lose billions."],[3445,3586,"What has she done to you?"],[3641,3728,"I have had your back"],[3728,3841,"from the beginning."],[3891,3999,"Stay the fuck away"],[3999,4141,"from my wife and daughter."]],"50":[[108,179,"Your wife!"],[250,346,"Emily's my wife,"],[346,475,"Selena's my daughter."],[500,621,"Touch them again"],[621,750,"and you'll regret it."],[750,934,"Anyone else want to try?"],[1230,1305,"Let's go."],[1380,1493,"You're going to regret this."],[1568,1668,"You all will."],[2594,2660,"This is on me."],[2698,2840,"I should have been watching out for you."],[2869,2998,"Even at the office."],[2998,3174,"What do you say we take a trip?"],[3174,3303,"Get away from all this."],[3303,3445,"You're anywhere you want."],[3445,3528,"Selena, how is she?"],[3528,3628,"Is she really okay?"],[3628,3778,"She's tougher than you think."],[3807,3949,"Tyler took her to say goodbye to her friend."],[3949,4049,"She'll be back soon."],[4099,4158,"Okay."],[4158,4254,"Speak of the devil and"],[4254,4366,"they're probably back now."],[4366,4408,"Hey."],[4408,4567,"Boss, we got attacked."],[4567,4621,"Selena's gone."],[4621,4692,"What?"]],"51":[[37,183,"Find her! I'm on my way."],[183,221,"No."],[221,262,"No, no, no."],[262,329,"This is my fault."],[329,408,"She's still recovering."],[408,437,"I don't know..."],[437,475,"Emily,"],[475,579,"listen to me."],[579,646,"Stay here."],[646,767,"Don't leave the house."],[767,888,"I'll bring her back, I promise."],[888,992,"But I need you to be safe."],[992,1113,"Promise me."],[1651,1701,"Hello?"],[1701,1860,"I sent the location."],[1860,1956,"Come alone"],[1956,2189,"or you'll only get her dead body!"],[2519,2673,"Mark I'm sorry."],[2673,2781,"I owe you more than"],[2781,2961,"I can ever repay you."],[2961,3140,"No matter what happens."],[3140,3340,"I love you, Emily."],[3803,3953,"Selena! Oh my god."],[3953,4037,"Baby are you ok?"],[4037,4099,"It's gonna be ok."],[4166,4216,"That's ok."],[4446,4525,"Anna?"],[4608,4721,"Why?"]],"52":[[0,100,"Anna?"],[166,283,"Why?"],[283,400,"Who else would want to deal with"],[400,550,"somebody as worthless as you?"],[596,746,"Do you really think that Mark's"],[746,859,"going to keep you?"],[859,967,"Do you really think that killing me"],[967,1126,"will fix your pathetic life?"],[1126,1322,"No, I'm not just killing you."],[1405,1530,"Selena too."],[1685,1856,"Consider it a package deal."],[2606,2736,"Emily and I..."],[2990,3123,"We knew each other."],[3561,3599,"You should have"],[3599,3716,"stayed in your lane."],[3741,3837,"It's too late now!"]],"53":[[725,796,"Emily!"],[1326,1413,"I'm fine, I'm fine."],[1459,1584,"Selena, get Selena."],[1747,1893,"Okay, it's okay, it's okay."],[2006,2110,"Mom, behind you!"],[2152,2373,"I'm taking you with me, you bitch!"],[3624,3787,"Mark, please don't leave me."]],"54":[[166,387,"I've messed up so much, Mark."],[387,546,"Please wake up."],[546,704,"We need you."],[704,913,"I won't let anything keep us apart again."],[1288,1547,"You're awake. I'll go get Dr. Grey."],[1547,1710,"Emily, wait."],[1881,2022,"I remember."],[2085,2198,"What?"],[2198,2431,"20 years ago..."],[2431,2635,"you had good news."],[2635,2790,"I never made it."],[2790,3069,"The accident took everything."],[3069,3345,"My memories."],[3345,3432,"My face."],[3432,3645,"My God. It's really you?"],[3645,3862,"All this time?"],[3862,4029,"I thought I lost you."],[4029,4258,"My family sent me to Switzerland"],[4258,4462,"for reconstructive surgery."],[4462,4662,"By the time I recovered,"],[4662,4783,"I couldn't remember anything."],[4917,5080,"I never thought fate would"],[5080,5251,"bring me back to you."],[5330,5497,"Hand me my coat?"],[6948,7157,"All this time."],[7157,7240,"it's really you."],[7240,7444,"It's always been you."]],"55":[[0,216,"All this time,"],[216,300,"It's really you."],[300,437,"It's always been you."],[437,738,"I'm so sorry. I should have been here."],[738,934,"I never should've left you alone."],[934,1105,"That's okay."],[1130,1184,"You're here now."],[1184,1313,"That's all that matters."],[1368,1493,"Where's Selena? She okay?"],[1493,1626,"Yes, she's next door."],[1626,1693,"She's shaken up,"],[1693,1789,"but the doctors are"],[1789,1939,"keeping her for observation."],[1939,2081,"Let's go see her."],[2081,2160,"Yeah."],[2640,2702,"You again?"],[2702,2794,"What the hell do you want now?"],[2794,2986,"Just thought you'd like to know the truth."],[2986,3053,"She's been lying"],[3053,3236,"to you this whole time."],[3236,3315,"After your money,"],[3315,3524,"she's playing you for a fool."],[3741,3874,"She ain't yours, buddy."],[3874,3966,"This proves it."],[3966,4141,"Selena is not yours."]],"56":[[0,196,"Selena is not yours."],[233,271,"This..."],[271,483,"This is a lie. This file is fake."],[533,759,"William, tell the truth."],[759,838,"You know I like it"],[838,980,"when you're feisty with me."],[1021,1080,"Hey!"],[1080,1201,"Let go of me!"],[1422,1522,"No! Mark!"],[1522,1618,"No!"],[1618,1693,"Haven't you done enough"],[1693,1789,"to ruin him?"],[1789,1972,"Nurse! Doctor! please!"],[1972,2181,"Save my fiancé!"],[2223,2331,"No!"],[2573,2644,"No!"],[3720,3807,"Dr. Grey?"],[3807,3933,"What's happening?"]],"57":[[0,179,"Her condition is deteriorating."],[179,287,"She needs a bone"],[287,458,"marrow transplant fast."],[458,533,"Please I'll do anything!"],[533,604,"Just save her."],[621,850,"We need a marrow transplant first."],[930,1117,"We'll call you once we find one."],[2344,2489,"Hey beautiful."],[2489,2610,"Long time no see."],[2852,2911,"You again?"],[2911,2998,"Give it back."],[3253,3370,"You married a billionaire and this"],[3370,3470,"is all that you got?"],[3557,3616,"No."],[3712,3816,"I want all your cash."],[3816,3928,"It's for Selena's treatment."],[3928,3987,"Give it back."],[4008,4154,"Still taking care of that little bastard."],[4154,4254,"Why don't you just let her die?"],[4671,4717,"Give me!"],[4746,4879,"Still got that fire in you, huh?"],[4979,5109,"I like that. You want to work off"],[5109,5201,"your debt another way?"],[5334,5459,"Let go of me!"],[5718,5826,"You're always cheap."],[5826,5876,"Help!"],[6281,6368,"Sorry I'm late."]],"58":[[33,125,"It's over."],[300,400,"Get up!"],[583,667,"Get off me!"],[788,930,"Eve's in custody as well for"],[930,1051,"orchestrating Selena's Kidnap."],[1051,1205,"William isn't Selena's father."],[1205,1288,"I know."],[1288,1463,"I never bought that bullshit."],[1463,1589,"But even if Selena isn't mine."],[1589,1747,"I'd still love the both of you,"],[1747,1868,"always."],[1868,1972,"You must worried about Selena."],[1972,2131,"I'll take you to the hospital."],[2302,2565,"Mr. Cardmond, I have great news"],[2565,2644,"your bone marrow"],[2644,2852,"is a perfect match for Selena."],[2852,3040,"The DNA test confirms that"],[3040,3274,"Selena's your biological daughter."],[3424,3532,"If you're ready,"],[3582,3645,"we can get started"],[3645,3757,"on the surgery right away."],[3757,3941,"Thank you so much, Dr. Grey."],[3941,4141,"You're more than welcome."],[4141,4275,"Congratulations."],[4479,4579,"Mark."],[4579,4725,"No one’s tearing us apart again."],[4725,4808,"No."],[5905,6018,"Oh my god!"],[6018,6131,"I caught it!"],[6272,6343,"Let's not rush into"],[6343,6481,"another wedding too soon, okay?"],[6481,6548,"Yeah, let's just"],[6548,6669,"enjoy the moment."]]}